Package gamelogic

Class Vec2D

  • java.lang.Object
    • gamelogic.Vec2D
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable
    public class Vec2D
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    An instance of the Vec2D class is a 2D vector with integer coordinates. Some basic operations for these vectors are implemented, such as addition, substraction, equality testing, dot product, etc.
